name: Primavera.1
description:
Today we celebrate the new year of nature! The Vernal (spring) Equinox!
In Brazil the popular name of this plant and the spring season are the same: "Primavera". The Primavera is a native plant from south america, very common to find at our houses, streets and in nature. In this photo we also see the little "Arapuá" (Trigona spinipes) polinating the flower.


ID: Bougainvillea spp.
